    EventForFirstPhase

  • Class Summary

    Event that carries the choice of where and which level to build

    This event represents the color chosen by the client

    Event that carries the God chosen by the player

    MoveChoice

    NumberOfPlayers
    Event that carries the number of player of the game, this is chose by the user who creates the match

    WorkerChoice
